{"tid":40352,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"逾6成雞肉產品樣本含耐藥性細菌　消委會籲煮熟才吃","createTime":"2016-12-15T07:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T07:01:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca3969f1893d7827967d6c1eaed27d0eeef3d07e","tid":40352,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:01:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1302500-20161215.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1302500-20161215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GGGiYPPtA8EOj5XwuKnxk3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=fa3014f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1302500-20161215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=234275cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1302500-20161215.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n逾6成雞肉產品樣本含耐藥性細菌　消委會籲煮熟才吃<br />\n2016-12-15 HKT 12:32<br />\n 分享工具\t facebook  twitter<br />\n 消委會呼籲市民食雞時，要完全煮熟。（張浩賢攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1302500_1_L_20161215130747.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1302500_1_L_20161215130747.jpg&h=bb629fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消委會呼籲市民食雞時，要完全煮熟。（張浩賢攝）<br />\n   00:00     <br />\n 00:00      <br />\n仇志榮報道<br />\n消委會首次測試市面100款雞肉產品，發現62%樣本含耐藥性細菌，廣泛用作治療「細菌性感染」疾病的抗生素都失效。<br />\n<br />\n消委會促請停止濫用抗生素，市民食雞時，要完全煮熟。"}]}